OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer faces pressure to set
OL,7,Fout plans to quit Downing Street over
OL,8,Fthe weekend after Andy Burnham stormed
OL,9,Fto victory in the Makerfield by-
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister has repeatedly
OL,13,Fvowed to fight any leadership
OL,14,Fchallenge, insisting he will not "walk
OL,15,Faway".
OL,17,FBut Mr Burnham's by-election victory
OL,18,Fhas prompted more backbenchers and
OL,19,FLabour grandees to call for Sir Keir
OL,20,Fto stand down.
OL,26,@vD@bOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
