PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781923667
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FSome MPs who had signed a statement
OL,7,Frejecting calls for a leadership
OL,8,Felection last month have now reversed
OL,9,Ftheir position while former home
OL,10,Fsecretary Alan Johnson told LBC his
OL,11,Fmessage to the Prime Minister would
OL,12,Fbe: "It's over, Keir."
OL,14,FSir Keir is understood to have spoken
OL,15,Fto a number of Cabinet ministers on
OL,16,FFriday, some of whom are reported to
OL,17,Fhave told him he should set out a
OL,18,Ftimetable for his departure.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
