OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FIt is understood that Mr Burnham's
OL,7,Fcamp wants Sir Keir to set out his
OL,8,Fplans in the coming days but would
OL,9,Faccept a timetable that kept him in No
OL,10,F10 until September.
OL,12,FBut former deputy leader Baroness
OL,13,FHarriet Harman has urged the party to
OL,14,Fmove faster, telling Sky News's
OL,15,FElectoral Dysfunction podcast
OL,16,Fministers could not be left "in a
OL,17,Fstate of paralysis all through the
OL,18,Fsummer".
OL,26,@xD@]OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
