OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781923667
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FMeanwhile, former home secretary Alan
OL,7,FJohnson told LBC that the Prime
OL,8,FMinister now has to step aside.
OL,10,FHe said: "I'd say it's over, Keir. And
OL,11,Flisten, he's a bright guy. He knows
OL,12,Fit's over. He will forever be in the
OL,13,Fhistory books as the man who turned us
OL,14,Faround, Labour, from the second-worst
OL,15,Fresult in our history to the second
OL,16,Fbest result in our history in one five-
OL,17,Fyear period."
OL,26,@rD@JOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
