OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781923667
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FBut Sir Keir appeared to be digging
OL,7,Fin, warning Labour staffers during a
OL,8,Fcall on Friday lunchtime to avoid
OL,9,F"plunging our party and our country
OL,10,Finto chaos by turning on each other
OL,11,Fand tearing apart our party and our
OL,12,Fmovement".
OL,14,FIt is understood he has also amassed a
OL,15,Fcampaign war chest to fight any
OL,16,Fleadership challenge with the backing
OL,17,Fof a group of private donors, as first
OL,18,Freported by The Times.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
