OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FFundraising has ramped up in the last
OL,7,Ftwo days with total pledges running
OL,8,Finto six figures, sources said.
OL,10,FSir Keir and his backers in the
OL,11,FParliamentary Labour Party have also
OL,12,Fstressed the need to focus on the by-
OL,13,Felection for the Greater Manchester
OL,14,Fmayoralty triggered by Mr Burnham's
OL,15,Felection.
OL,17,FThat by-election is scheduled to take
OL,18,Fplace on July 30, with Labour set to
OL,19,Fannounce its candidate on June 26.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
