OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781923667
OL,3,CStarmer under pressure to quit after
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election win
OL,6,FThe party is already pitching the
OL,7,Fcontest as a two-horse race between
OL,8,FLabour and Reform UK but the Greens
OL,9,Fwill look to build on their success in
OL,10,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election with
OL,11,Fa strong challenge of their own.
OL,13,FGreen leader Zack Polanski has sought
OL,14,Fto portray his party as the main
OL,15,Fchallenger to Nigel Farage, saying the
OL,16,Fmayoral contest will be "a straight up
OL,17,Fbattle between the Green Party vs
OL,18,FReform".
OL,26,@xD@YOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
